{"tid":360904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林子健報稱不適　召救護車送院","createTime":"2017-08-15T16:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T23:57:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e1af0fc057406a98006c05c1577651a9f668dc","tid":360904,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170816/large/1502813917_92a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170816%2Flarge%2F1502813917_92a2.jpg&h=fa1d4b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【23:55更新】於紅磡警署扣查的林子健報稱不適，召救護車送院<br />\n<br />\n【22:51更新】林子健不准保釋，將於紅磡警署通宵扣查<br />\n<br />\n【19:05更新】林子健由探員陪同乘警車離開西九總部，再押返紅磡警署<br />\n<br />\n【19:00更新】警方消息，林子健報稱在旺角被人擄走當天，其實是在旺角區自行搭紅頂小巴前往西貢，他上車時未見有人脅逼他<br />\n<br />\n【18:40更新】消息稱，林子健昨晚被捕，帶往警署辦理完手續後，至今日凌晨5時許獲准休息，至中午時份，警方替他錄取口供，據悉林子健全程保持緘默，其間有律師陪同<br />\n<br />\n【18:35更新】據悉，警方連同法醫替林子健再驗傷，並會做錄影口供<br />\n<br />\n【17:20更新】林子健於下午約4時50分，由警員帶上警車離開紅磡警署，前往西九龍警察總部。其間林坐在車尾中間位置，雙手被鎖上手銬，亦沒有戴上頭套，任由傳媒拍攝其容貌"},{"pid":"4fdc22c06d4c7b8cd4105d00cab936f446a03486","tid":360904,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170816&amp;guid=57086217&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170816%26guid%3D57086217%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=kTTBxhKuG1eO8%2BXVsyK9Ql0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=02733f90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170816%26guid%3D57086217%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=36c17140\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170816&amp;guid=57086217&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"52a8198a37330647c3f912119eb